          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏大王：依臣之见，将李广打入天牢；然后兴动人马，杀上他邦，夺取他国"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花花世界，有何难哉？"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家此言差也！从前原许年年进贡，岁岁往朝。至今三载，无宝奉上；又要兴"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "兵杀上他邦，情理难容。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王说话懦无刚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "匡罢言来听端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打一封战表到他邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "难当为臣化龙枪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将李广打入天牢内"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他国纵有千员将"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家错把本奏上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王言来听端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人心归附周文王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "封孤北海为帝王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军中无粮箭怎放？"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "饥饿焉能手提枪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不做一国丧乱王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "纣王无道乾坤丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "武王伐纣乾坤掌"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宁做一个太平犬"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军中无粮去放抢，"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打劫民间自有粮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "挂榜安民免钱粮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "争下江山大王掌"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿家奏本性情犟，"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "细听孤王说端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大战他国彩云庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "降书降表到他邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕的是马到临崖难收缰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从前邓虎兴兵将"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久战不胜把命丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劝卿家休要性情犟"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一言提起邓虎将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "背转身来自思量："
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何况今日少栋梁！"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再与大王作商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "从前邓虎兴兵将"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "久战不胜把命丧"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "劝卿家休要性情犟"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "依大王之见？"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "邓虎老将不能抗"
        },
        {
          "character": "匡罢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回头我把二本上"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且听探马一报。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忙将李广催贡事，报与我国大王知。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启奏大王：天朝李广前来催贡，已到十里长亭。请旨定夺！"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿站立两厢，听孤令下！"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王忙把旨传降，"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两班文武听端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "顺者昌来逆者亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "辽太",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情理相待比杀砍强。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
